  "title": "Electrical Project Engineer #79944",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Electrical Engineering/ Consultancy</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Project Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Paya Lebar (near MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday - Friday (8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Transport Allowance + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and prepare technical specifications for electrical systems and installations.</li><li>Conduct on-site evaluations of Low Tension (LT) and High Tension (HT) electrical setups in accordance with Energy Market Authority (EMA) regulations.</li><li>Support Professional Engineers (PE) and Licensed Electrical Workers (LEW) in performing switching operations on electrical panels.</li><li>Be on standby to respond to urgent service calls at client facilities, ensuring prompt and effective resolution of electrical issues.</li><li>Draft incident summaries, technical assessments, and proposal documents.</li><li>Oversee and coordinate subcontractors during scheduled maintenance tasks, ensuring compliance with safety and quality standards.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Electrical Engineering or a related discipline (recognized by EMA for application of LEW).</li><li>At least 1-2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Possess Class 3 driving license is an added advantage.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79944 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
